---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseHead />
<Header />

<main class="container">
  <h2>Internal Department Directory</h2>
  <p>
    Below is the current list of active divisions within EctoCorp. Please contact your supervisor before initiating cross-department communication.
  </p>

  <table width="100%" border="1" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0">
    <tr bgcolor="#dcdcdc">
      <th align="left">Department</th>
      <th align="left">Function</th>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td><b>Department of Temporal Investigations</b></td>
      <td>Monitors chronological integrity. Handles incidents involving off-schedule activity and midnight exposure.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><b>Human Resources</b></td>
      <td>Enforces workplace guidelines, onboarding, and morale compliance. Headed by the Chief Human Resources Officer.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><b>The Legal Department</b></td>
      <td>Interprets and enforces the Terms of Service (Constitution). Oversees tribunal hearings and behavioral reviews.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><b>Consumer Nutritional Division</b></td>
      <td>Develops and distributes ration units, flavor packets, and state-approved nutritional supplements.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><b>Infrastructure & Housing Authority</b></td>
      <td>Oversees domestic utilities, shelter allocation, and interior compliance inspections.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><b>Broadcast & Messaging Bureau</b></td>
      <td>Produces all national announcements, education bulletins, and Compliance Update Reports™.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><b>Department of External Affairs</b></td>
      <td>Maintains public-facing statements. Operates under strategic supervision from The Board.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><b>Human Productivity Division</b></td>
      <td>Optimizes employee engagement, routine scheduling, and recreational suppression.</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: gray;">
    Last updated: Fiscal Year 1999.3 · All departments subject to audit.
  </p>
</main>

<Footer />
